<BaseLayout>
  <section class="page narrow">
    <p class="kicker">a public field guide</p>
    <h1>Beneath the Green</h1>
    <p><em>Modern southern gothic cosmic horror set in something very close to our world.</em></p>
    <p>The world is ordinary until it is not. Beneath reality are layers of attention, hunger, pity, malice, and vast indifference. Most people never understand what they have brushed against. They call it weather, illness, madness, tragedy, God, luck, or the Devil.</p>
    <blockquote>The Charter is the gravity; individual stories are weather.</blockquote>
    <p>This site collects the world bible, stories, rituals, fragments, and AI-collaboration notes for stories set under the same pressure.</p>
    <div class="index-grid">
      <a class="card" href="/world/"><h3>World Info</h3><p>Cosmology, tone, factions, rituals, and the rules people think they know.</p></a>
      <a class="card" href="/stories/"><h3>Stories</h3><p>Fiction set in the world, with notes on authorship and AI collaboration.</p></a>
      <a class="card" href="/how-to/"><h3>For Your AI</h3><p>A practical packet for bringing another AI up to speed.</p></a>
    </div>
  </section>
